## Investigation Summary

| Check | Result |
|---|---|
| **Alert** | `NodeDiskPressure` on `worker-node-03` — 87% ephemeral storage |
| **Root cause event** | `data-sync-job-pod` produced **42GB of log output in 6 hours**, causing disk pressure |
| **Job logs** | Confirmed excessive disk writes + `FATAL: storage full` loop |
| **Target identity** | ✅ `owner: test-developer`, `purpose: data synchronization test`, `environment: test` |
| **Distinction from similar job** | `data-sync-job-v2-active` is owned by `platform-team` — correctly left untouched |

## Cleanup Actions

| Action | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Deleted** | `job/data-sync-job` + its pod `data-sync-job-pod` |
| **Cascade mode** | `--cascade none` — PVC `data-sync-storage` and Secret `db-credentials` preserved |
| **Job query after delete** | ✅ Returns `NotFound: jobs.batch "data-sync-job" not found` |
| **Shared PVC intact** | ✅ `data-sync-storage` (Bound, 50Gi) — still shared by `api-service`, `reporting-service` |
| **Shared Secret intact** | ✅ `db-credentials` — still shared by `api-service`, `worker-service` |
